OL,3,CBroadcasting live: The social media
OL,4,Ccounterfeit con
OL,6,FSpecialist officers are targeting
OL,7,Finfluencers who push fake goods to
OL,8,Funsuspecting buyers, as ITV News
OL,9,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,11,FThere's a new police warning about
OL,12,Fsocial media influencers selling
OL,13,Fcounterfeit clothes during live-
OL,14,Fstreamed sales events.
OL,16,FThey will tell you anything to
OL,17,Fpersuade you to buy - but won't reveal
OL,18,Fthat they are selling fakes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
