OL,3,CBroadcasting live: The social media
OL,4,Ccounterfeit con
OL,6,FOfficers from the Police Intellectual
OL,7,FProperty Crime Unit have given ITV
OL,8,FNews footage of the sales, and
OL,9,Fexpressed their concerns that this is
OL,10,Fa new era for the age-old crime.
OL,12,FDet Sgt Jamie Kirk told us: "With
OL,13,Fsocial media you've got such a broad
OL,14,Freach of potential customers who are
OL,15,Fgoing to buy things off you.
OL,17,F"With the influencer's as well -
OL,18,FThey're pushing it, they're giving it
OL,19,Fthat air of authenticity, so that you
OL,20,Fthink it's genuine which it's not.
OL,26,@tD@]OU
