OL,3,CBroadcasting live: The social media
OL,4,Ccounterfeit con
OL,6,F"You are buying counterfeit goods."
OL,8,FPolice images of a warehouse full of
OL,9,Fcounterfeit fashion highlight this new
OL,10,Fand growing trend.
OL,12,FThe criminals often broadcast live on
OL,13,Fsocial media sites from their
OL,14,Fwarehouses.JCampaigners are worried
OL,15,Fthat the persuasive skills of
OL,16,Finfluencers will make counterfeits
OL,17,F"cool".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@FO]
