OL,3,CBroadcasting live: The social media
OL,4,Ccounterfeit con
OL,6,FSarah Woodcock from the Anti-slavery
OL,7,Fcollective spoke to ITV News, "We've
OL,8,Fseen this huge attitudinal shift,
OL,9,Fespecially among Gen Z, who are buying
OL,10,Fmore counterfeit goods with absolutely
OL,11,Fno concern for how that looks.
OL,13,F"It has become entirely normalised.
OL,15,F"So I think the social media
OL,16,Finfluencers have really played a big
OL,17,Fpart in that.
OL,26,@oD@_OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
