OL,3,CBroadcasting live: The social media
OL,4,Ccounterfeit con
OL,6,F"They're the ones who are basically
OL,7,Fsaying these products are okay, you
OL,8,Fcan buy them, you can wear them, and
OL,9,Fno one will think any less so for
OL,10,Fdoing so."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FEmma Duncan, who unknowingly who
OL,18,Fbought pirated goods via social media,
OL,19,Fis determined to warn others.
