OL,4,Ccounterfeit con
OL,6,F"I am really cautious and I've been
OL,7,Fopened up to how many sites there are
OL,8,Fthat are fake," she told ITV News.
OL,10,FSocial media platforms say they have
OL,11,Feffective tools for detecting and
OL,12,Fremoving counterfeits - with TikTok
OL,13,Falone saying it's taken down 40
OL,14,Fmillion items.
OL,16,FPolice say the goods are fake but the
OL,17,Fproblem is real - as one of the oldest
OL,18,Fcrimes links up to one of the most
OL,19,Fmodern sales techniques.
